<p>Freedom and liberty? That's great!! Sincerely, you made my day, thank you very much ^^<br>Adapt censorship, arrest people who are making questions, kill cultural and religious minorities and force an integration of Han culture everywhere in the country is freedom?<br>No doubt you consider the caustic relation between east and west as a mere form of racism...</p>

</div>

<span class="post-media"><ul data-role="post-media-list"></ul></span>
</div>
</div>
