<div class="post-body-inner">

<div class="post-message-container" data-role="message-container">

<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>"As long as America is willing to counterbalance China, they won't roll over.<br>The minute America is gone, they will."</p><p>Thus, China's armaments buildup in weapons and technology specifically aimed at U.S military vulnerabilities.</p>

</div>

