<p>You realize that Mexico attacked US forces first, right?</p><p>Might have noticed, The Philippines aren't a US State or Territory. Puerto Rico keeps voting down independence.</p><p>But you really need to live in today's world, and leave the Soviet style 'whataboutism' behind.</p><p>Unless that's what you are getting paid to do.</p>

