<p>Ah, since you side-stepped, the answer is</p><p> -none-</p><p>Lesson is, don't start killing you can't finish the job.</p><p>Mexico got the war they wanted.</p><p>But once again, Mexico lost, in  no small part to Santa Anna</p><p>Could have negotiated, but 'Honor' wouldn't have that.</p>

