<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>So your solution is to continue shrugging off terrible acts because others have done them before?<br>Is it not possible that the world as a whole is now trying to set a better standard of behavior? China has had its imperialist moments before too: Xinjiang, Tibet, its foray into Vietnam and decades of propping up North Korea, even clashing with India in the southern Himalayas.</p>

