<span class="post-byline">

<span class="author publisher-anchor-color"><a href="#" data-action="profile" data-user="28101669" data-username="r0b50" data-role="username">r0b50</a></span>






<span><a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2014/11/chinas-dangerous-game/380789/#comment-1633260837" class="parent-link" data-role="parent-link"><i aria-hidden="true" class="icon-forward" title="in reply to"></i> YourSupremeCommander</a></span>

