<div class="post-body-inner">

<div class="post-message-container" data-role="message-container">

<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>The majority of inter-state conflicts are resolved through negotiations and treaties. The statement is meaningless and misleading and mischaracterizes the substantive nature of the conflict itself by focusing on a pointless digression. How many negotiations *aren't* peaceful? I can't help but think that this is intentional obfuscation on your part.</p>

</div>

