<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>Dismissing other people's opinion just because it does not gel with your preconceived notion is unproductive.  There is actually a peer-reviewed comprehensive study on China's border management done by a political scientist in MIT and it paints a very different picture than the popular belief of an expansionist China.</p><p><a href="http://press.princeton.edu/chapters/i8782.html" rel="nofollow">http://press.princeton.edu/cha...</a></p><p>The study is some what dated (published in 2008) but the main points in the study remain valid.</p>

</div>

