</span>


</header>


<div class="post-body-inner">

<div class="post-message-container" data-role="message-container">

<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>I wonder what his opinion would be if China were to offer full independence based off of a free and fair vote such as the one Scotland just had.  I really mean that, I have no idea what his opinion would be.</p>

</div>

