<div class="post-body-inner">

<div class="post-message-container" data-role="message-container">

<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>Outer Mongolia is culturally and politically influenced by their ties to the old USSR, but today is basically an economic satrap of the PRC. Russia doesn't need their resources- China does. Tibet, similarly, has all it's logistical and business ties to the Chinese metropolitan core, and would still be under their economic domination were it "independent".</p>

</div>

