<div class="post-message-container" data-role="message-container">

<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>Even if the Indians could have voted, were outnumbered, not that the Chippewa and Sioux would agree on much of anything</p><p>When Minnesota became a State, there were approximate 30k Indians to 150k Settlers , growing from 6k a decade earlier when it became a territory, having the same Indian population.</p>

</div>

