<p><i>What are you talking about? You confused km with nautical miles. I pointed that out. </i></p><p>You seem to have me confused with someone else.</p><p><i>BTW, both the Taiwanese government and the PRC claim that Taiwan is part of China.</i></p><p>Of course, they don't agree about what exactly that means, or who is the legitimate political authority, or did you also conveniently forget the last 60 odd years of history?</p>

