<p>I quote the US military historian James Calvin</p><p><a href="http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/library/report/1984/CJB.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.globalsecurity.org/...</a></p><p>"There may well have been room for compromise over these issues, but [stubbornness] and India’s aggressive forward policy resulted in armed conflict."</p>

