<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>I'm not so sure.  Tell all the Africans currently benefiting from Chinese-built roads and infrastructure that China has no "soft power" or diplomacy.</p><p>While the US has been tromping around the world littering smart bombs in it's wake, China's been making friends with a lot of people.  Just not so much with its immediate neighbors.</p>

</div>

<span class="post-media"><ul data-role="post-media-list"></ul></span>
</div>
</div>
<a class="see-more hidden" title="see more" data-action="see-more">see more</a>
</div>

