<blockquote>...smoke filled biker...bars...</blockquote><p></p><p>Heh, that's a nice analogy.  It reminds me of the time I swaggering into The Bashful Bandit in Tucson and slapped 2 quarters on the pool table and shouted, "Who's next, a$$---es?"</p><p>I'm just kidding.  I only fantasized about doing that every time I drove by it.</p>

