<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>Yup.  And we could use a shape to describe that co-prosperity.  A sphere perhaps.  A sphere of co-prosperity.  And since it is in the east, we'll add that word.  Then to make it sound snazzy, we'll toss in 'greater'</p><p>Greater East Asia Co-Prosperity Sphere.</p><p>Has a ring to it.</p>

</div>

