<span class="post-meta">
<span class="bullet time-ago-bullet" aria-hidden="true">•</span>


<a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2014/11/chinas-dangerous-game/380789/#comment-1633760773" data-role="relative-time" class="time-ago" title="Monday, October 13, 2014 9:03 PM">4 days ago</a>

