<div class="post-body-inner">

<div class="post-message-container" data-role="message-container">

<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>1. No, testicles are not sine qua non for killing a lot of    <br>    people. There are many examples in history where a lot <br>    of killing was done by, or ordered by folks without a 'Y' <br>    chromosome; or even with a 'Y' chromosome but no <br>    testicles...<br>2. I used "testicles", the word, as a metaphor for resolute <br>    determination to do whatever is necessary, even if it <br>    involves killing a lot of people. Whether you like my <br>    metaphor or not, is your business, not mine; but thanks <br>    for sharing.<br>3. Don't flatter yourself that, expressing what you like or <br>    you don't like, regarding my beliefs, will make me want to<br>    express myself in a way that would meet your approval, <br>    and/or liking. But, again, if you feel the need to share, <br>    that is your prerogative, and I don't really mind.</p>

</div>

<span class="post-media"><ul data-role="post-media-list"></ul></span>
