<div class="post-body-inner">

<div class="post-message-container" data-role="message-container">

<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>I was on Palawan in May.  I spent a lot of time there as a matter of fact.  I did not see any Korean, Vietnamese or Chinese signs anywhere. I'm sure there must have been a few I did not notice, but nothing like the author claims.  The "rickshaws" he is talking about are called trikes, and they are ubiquitous in the Philippines.</p><p>I'm assuming the author is simply making this up to add to spice to his story.</p>

