<p>I agree with your post and appreciate your insight.  however, i tend to view the environment as China's major problem.  obviously this is connected with the economy of China, but I can't see how the degradation can continue into the future, even if the growth rate slows dramatically.  so much damage has already been done.</p><p>people will have to deal with the pollution long after the Party is booted out for a sluggish and corrupt economy...</p>

