<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>Barbaric and sinister Communist China <br>+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++</p><p>CHINESE AGRESSION MIRRORS PRE-1962 ERA</p><p>" China's expanding axis of evil with Pakistan, including a new troop presence in PoK, heightens India's vulnerability in Jammu and Kashmir, "</p><p>indiatoday . intoday . in/story/the-big-story/1/157740.html</p><p>CHINESE AGGRESSION IN SOUTH CHINA SEA INCREASING AS SHOTS FIRED</p><p>" According to NHK a Chinese naval ship fired warning shots at a Philippine fishing boat in the South China Sea in February. Senior officials in the Philippine government and military informed NHK of the incident."</p><p>www . japannewstoday . com/?p=4012</p><p>VIETNAM BLASTS CHINA AGGRESSION, DEMANDS COMPENSATION</p><p>" Vietnam’s Foreign Ministry on Friday staunchly opposed China over the previous day’s intrusion of three Chinese marine surveillance vessels deep into Vietnam’s continental shelf and their sabotage of the country’s economic operations "</p><p>english . thesaigontimes . vn/Home/society/nation/17201/</p>

</div>

