<div class="avatar hovercard">
<a href="http://disqus.com/MarkR307/" class="user" data-action="profile" data-username="MarkR307" data-user="24694335">
<img data-role="user-avatar" data-user="24694335" src="//a.disquscdn.com/1413230218/images/noavatar92.png" alt="Avatar">
