<div class="publisher-anchor-color" data-role="message-content">
<div class="post-message " data-role="message" dir="auto">

<p>Interesting isn't it? Remember just a few decades ago the Vietnamese were relying on China to prevent American aggression on their soil. At least today, China, unlike the US is not bombing the H out of them. You know it would be useful if you remembered which nation it was that killed 3 million Vietnamese not that long ago, before you start crticizing China. People in glass houses shouldn't throw stones!</p>

</div>

<span class="post-media"><ul data-role="post-media-list"></ul></span>
</div>
</div>
